Package: sigvar
Title: Quantify and visualize variability of mutational signatures within and across samples
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R: c(person("Maike", "Morrison", , "maikem@stanford.edu", role = c("aut"),
              comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0430-1401")),
            person("Nicolas", "Alcala", , "alcalan@iarc.who.int", role = c("aut", "cre"),
              comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5961-5064")))
Description: This package allows to import mutational signature attribution (a.k.a. exposure) matrices and compute, visualize, and test their variabilities within and across samples.
